uring transition to a gauge symmetry broken phase where the scalar dark energy\ndensity approaches zero without fine tuning; the gauge symmetry breakdown is\nachieved without tachyonic mass term in the action.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2006 08:37:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
